Summary: Found object via map in bible, searching for Noah's Ark.following ground markers led to this.
divs: Sighting Detailsi located this from a map put out by dean coomes @ bible-codes.org.it led me here .it is marked on the earth so as to be able to locate it.i will send coordinates.it is round and had 2 square items on side of it,like an igloo.it blends in to back ground.8200-8600 feet.i was hurt hiking to it,sprained knees.aerial view only.it may be the seed pod of noah
